text: Émilie Loit was the defending champion, but did not compete this year. Lucie Šafářová won the title by defeating Li Na 6–7(4–7), 6–4, 6–3 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Finals=== ===Top Half=== ===Bottom Half=== ==References== * Main and Qualifying Draws (WTA) Category:2005 Estoril Open
